results.description:
Hand-painted, one-of-a-kind Happy Rock - "LIFE."    This beautiful rock was found on the coast of North Carolina.  This beautiful little rock is quartz-like in appearance. No two rocks are alike - nature intended it that way!  They are oddly shaped and have spots and holes and cracks and variations in color and each one is beautiful! 

Happy Rocks add fun and whimsy to your decor - boldly displayed on a coffee table or bookshelf or windowsill; more subtly displayed in nooks and crannies and corners; and around your plants and meditation altar.  Happy Rocks are the perfect one-of-a-kind gift.  Thinner/flatter rocks often do well on an easel.  Smaller rocks - pocket rocks - can be carried with you to offer comfort, positive energy and good vibes everywhere you go.  Interested in a custom rock?  Message me!

This Happy Rock measures approximately 2" x 1 1/4".

All rocks are sprayed with clear Rustoleum lacquer.

* Shipment is generally 3 to 5 business days.

Also Be sure to check out our 2nd Etsy shop which includes color creations from the use of our LED UV flatbed https://www.etsy.com/shop/SignsForExpressions?ref=hdr_shop_menu

Two contrasting colors of paint are applied, the design is laser engraved, a fine hairline is applied to the design which gives an awesome touch. The final touches are completed once it goes through our antiquing process with edges distressed.

*When working with wood and the antiquing process, each sign has its own warmth and charm. While we try to get the best wood at the lumber yard, sometimes there will be knots or other slight imperfections in the wood, this is considered adding character to the rustic style of this line of our signs. Thanks for stopping by our shop and please do not hesitate to ask any questions.
